values: I jus got in from talkin to Brian....and he's bein funny today.Anyways,there's this guy Kyle in my World History class who likes me and keeps telling me and he's also in Brian's 3d period class.I don't like Kyle but he likes me and has since last year....he wont give up.This sucks,Kyle keeps tellin me to dump Brian and go out with him,when i love Brian.I dont plan on dumping Brian anyime soon...at all!Im soooo bored.

well its been awhile since iv updated this and i thought it waz about time.Well now im in the 10th grade and have a b/f,i got back wit Brian...he lives right nextdoor to me now so...yeah its awesome.Ambers bein a lil bitch right now tryin to control who i can be friends wit becuz me and Lindsey,this girl Amber hates,are friends.Amber and Lindsey use to be friends but Amber killed the friendship by bein a 
phsyco-control bitch and hitting on Lindsey's b/f.Oh,hey i got another therapist too.My mom thinks im too angry and violent for some1 my age.lol.My b/f Brian is so sweet.I swear he'd do just about anything for me.I love him so much,the weird part is i'v never felt this way bout or with anyother person.

Well todays my birthday,doesnt really feel like anything special.Just another boring day like all the rest,that's what it feels like to me.We're celebrating tomorrow wih my friends and then sunday all the guys are coming over to hang out.Today was really boring,yes yes i know i complain alot I've already gotten afew emails telling me what a shitty person I am because i complain alot in my journal.Well it's my journal and I can do what ever the fuck I feel like in here so...Sorry if they dont like they dont have to read it.
Well i got to go.Byez

Well,Amber's over at my house and Greg's in some kind of a mood.He's getting on my nurves tonight,but I'll get over it.He
says he's in a state of depression,because his levels are unbalenced.Which,I actually believe him but he doesn't have to take it out on me,just because I asked a stupid question.I am so fed up with alot of people in my life,that doesn't include Greg right now.He's just getting on my nurves alittle bit,but I mean,everyone gets on everyone's nurves every now and then.Right?I'm bored..Amber's spending the night to night then tomorrow we're going to Sound Idea for a punk rock concert.There's suppose to be three bands playing,it should be fun.Amber and I are going together and then I'm spending the night at her house till saturday.
Why do I even write?!?No body even f#cking comments anymore. No one cares,and I'm suppose to give a flying f#ck about what other people say?Yeah,ok?

I am so ready to leave this place,this world,this school, these people....everything.Greg says I'm stupid for wanting to leave and for saying that no one cares for me,when in reality it's the truth.Greg doesn't live or go to school with me.I mean,Greg is one of my best friends but he doesn't get this part about me obviously.I get treated like crap all the time,no matter where I am.I am like a little bug that people either step on or over,either way it hurts.I am an un wanted thing.I could disapear for a week and I bet no one would notice or care.

Well,it's been a while since I've writen but alot has happened.I got Katie a boyfriend(YaY!!),she's going out with my other best friend Raymond.We all went to Katie's house on saturday and hung out for awhile,and all I'll say is we had "fun".LOL.Justin is such a sweet heart,tuesday I'm going to there house and then thursday I'm going to the drive in movies with Katie and Justin and both there mother's.I'm not sure what we're going to see yet,but i dont care as long as I'm not here at my house.I've never had a boyfriend that I've been as close to as I am with Justin,and honestly,that scares me.The fact that I'm so close to someone in such a short amount of time.I don't know what to make of the whole situation,but what a wonderful situation it is.I've never spent this much time with one of my boyfriends before either,so....

OMG.....I actually got a boy friend.I am so amaze!Not to mention the fact that he's adorably cute and sweet and....well
you know the rest.His name is Justin and he's my best friend's cousin.She has a live journal too,she's on my friends list.It's dhscougarpride if you want to see it some time.I'm going to his house saturday.We're going to have fun,me him and katie.

I'm at my aunts,baby sitting again.Well amber and Jenny are getting on my last nerve,they are so bitchy.I hope Jenny eats Amber then explodes.It'll serve them both right.I hate both of them,they got a whole crap load of there friends to yell at me and shit and I hate that.If they think there's a problem they should deal with it not have there friends do it for them.
Everythings falling apart and i can't do anything!!!!!!!!!!!!

Well,once again my sister's not here and my parents and my brother are at a baseball game,and I'm here alone.It doesn't feel to good this time,being alone and all.This time before my mom left,we got in a fight and I told my sister i hated her.Which was as close to the truth as I can get without being honest.I'm hating life,there's nothing good about mine.Everyone loves life,says "oh it's so wonderful and fun".Bull shit,life isn't fun or wonderful,it's depressing and hurtful.I can't stand being alone,and most of the time I am,mentally of course.None the less I'm alone.I wish I had someone who loved me and someone i could love back,but so far nobody has stepped out of the shadows.I'm so fucking depressed right now,I mean I don't know what to do,what not to do,or what to tell myself.I'v felt this way for what seems like forever,but I have nobody to tell.Nobody cares how I feel,or what happens to me.I'v given up hope on a normal life with people,and caring.
i dont know what to write.
OMG!Amber told something to my friend (exboyfriend)that she wasnt spose to and i am sorta mad at her.

I hate being here,at my house,I mean my prison.I'm tired of being treated like shit.I never get treated the way I deserve.I dont ask for much just alittle respect every now and then.I can't even get that.So I'm just gonna stop being involved with my family,it seems thats the only solution to my problem.

Well today I went to Disney World and it was awesome.It was really fun.I've really never enjoyed my self with my family as much as I did today.Well right now I'm back at my aunt's house and tomorrow we're going to Clear Water Beach.It should be really fun,I'm still in search of a boy friend and am wondering what is wrong with me.My friend Katrina tells me that there is absolutely nothing wrong with me,so obviously she needs her eyes,ears,or brain checked.Well,my cousins want me to go frog catching so I got to go.....As weird as that sounds.Byez.

Well,right now I'm at my friend Katrina's house.She's really nice but she's goin through a tough time with her boyfriend. He never takes the time to listen to her or have her over.As she says "he's too busy jacking Eric's (his best friend) winky".LOL. She is so in love with him,but he can be an ass to her sometimes. He's so mean,he invited her over to his house and then leaves after she gets there to go play with his best friend.He didn't even envite her to go with them,he just left her at his house!What an ass hole!She even bought him a wedding ring ,it cost $120,and they weren't even getting married.I've spent two days at her house and I'm going on three.We got to go four-wheeling through the orange groves and down some hidden trails.When we walked down to the bridge and looked over the side,we saw a whole human skeleton,but it was missing a few bones and there was a hat next to it.Then when we looked on the bank of the river we saw shotgun shells.It was really creepy,it looked like it had been there for a really long time because there was nothing but bones and a hat left to it.It was nasty.Well,she's depressed and I've got to go help her so,byez

I'm back at my aunts house again,which is cool cause she lets me do anything I want,
as long as it's legal and she doesn't get in trouble.We just got done eating burger king a little while ago.I wish I could live here,her house is simple and small.Easy to work with and live in,and we are so much alike,it's scary.I don't wish she was my mom though,because then our great relationship would be ruined my that whole mother daughter,never getting along,thing.I get to spend the night here again,and it's really weird how we enjoy each others company,but we hardly see each other.Do you think that's odd?I do.I might watch her kids tomorrow night while she goes on a date.Her two kids are so cute,Joey's ten and Josh's eight.They are such good kids and so easy to take care of.Well,I got to go,byez.

Right now I'm doing nothing but playing on the computer and watching my cousin play Vice City.We just got done eating and before that we were at the recreation pool.It's this really cool place that has a giant pool with a high dive and a low dive.I really like the high dive,you get a sort of rush when you jump.Sort of like bungy jumping with out the cord is what I'd immagin.I'm in one of those moods,you know,right on the line of sad or happy,one push and I'm gone to either side.It all depinds on the push to deturmine which side I'm going to.For some reason I'm listening to Eminem.Well I got to go,byez.

Right now I'm at my aunt's house watching her kids and the show Chalk Zone,for some very strange reason.Right now I'm sort of bored but it's fun,I guess.We just got done watching "The Cat In The Hat Movie",and I've got to say,it was probably the most stupid movie I've ever seen.It had abolutely nothing to do with the book what so ever.Well,Noel,she's one of those small mexican dogs,like on the taco bell commercials,is sitting on my lap.Well,now Flufferz,the cat is sitting beside me.This cat is huge and when I say huge I don't mean huge,I mean extraordinarily huge. Oh,wonderful,now the cat stuck it's fat ass in front of the computer and I can hardly see.My aunt lives in an apartment in tampa,it's not bad but it's not home.I mean I don't like being at home but at least that's were I belong.So far my spring break plans are all duds.Tanya's going to Alabama,Carol's going to Virginia,Amanda K. is grounded the whole break,and that only leaves a few people left to talk to and have over and go over to there houses.Well, I just looked down at my stuff just to see the cat licking the bottom of my slippers.Now he's attacking it.This cat scares me, badly.I think I'm going to go be scared away from the computer.Talk at you later,byez.

I asked Brian(my exboyfriend)out again and he's still thinking about it.He said he's got some one else on his mind right now,but he still doesn't know yet.So I'm keeping my fingers crossed.Him & his parents both envited me to the beach with them, and I'm hoping I'll be allowed to go.I don't know why I even broke up with him in the first place.That was a big mistake.Brian's probably one of the nicest boyfriends I'd ever had, and I'm hoping I'll have the chance to make up for that mistake.I really want to make up for what I did to him,seems how I did dump him the day after christmas.I don't even know why I did it, it was a really stupid mistake that I severely regret.I gave him the note monday morning and he still hasn't answered and it's driving me mad.
In my daydreams I sit and think how awsome it would be to fly away from the world,just for a little bit.How maybe just one true friend would worry about me,then I'd know who cared and who didn't.

I am actually ready before 6:40am!!!It's amazing,cause usually I'm struggling at last minute to get my shoes on or brush me teeth but not today.Today I am ready at 6:14am,so I've decided to right in my journal,which I've never done in the mornings on a week day.

It's Tuesday,and already I'm being btiched at and bitching at other's.My grandma was acting like she was my mother,and told me I have fucked up friends,because she heard Amber got her lip pierceing and dresses all in black.Well,if they think Amber's wierd,they need to take a long look at most of Amnda's friends.Then,it's not enough that they
criticized Amber,but then they went off on how terrible I am.
Ok,how do they have room to talk about me being such a terrible person when they're sitten there insulting and tearing me down!WTF!!!They need to stop being so hyporitical and get over there shit!!I defended Amber,who is my best friend,and that just made them even more mad

That's where my life going,down the shit hole!Me & this guy in  math class were joking around on the way to the car riders and I hit him with a book.Then he was just joking around,but he told Tonya that I hit him and she threatened to kick my ass.She's such a bitch.Oh,also,me and Amy are fighting again.She keeps ragging on my friend Carol.So I told her to back off and she's not.So we were bitching at each other in home room.Then she told me she could beat me up,and Carol said if she even breaths the wrong way at me Carol's going to kick her.....Well,you know the rest.

My life.What's left to say?It's the meaning of bored.God, nothing good or exciting ever happens to me,and when it does, something comes along and crushes it like a cockroach.Why is it nothing good happens to me,just everyone else.I don't really get it.I seem to be a magnet for the bad stuff in people's lives.I have very few close friends and the ones I have are the best ever,even though we do fight sometimes,but doesn't every one?Well got to go,byez.

Every night I wish I could just fade away,for some reason?Sometimes I just want to be invisible,and I don't know why I'm talking like this but it all just came to my mind.I'm kind of lonely, seems how I don't have a boyfriend any more   (which really sucks).Will I ever have a happy relationship with some.I wish I could just get close to some one for a long time.I think it'll take a while before that wish will come true,don't you?I think I'm going through that "feeling sorry for yourself" stage.There's alot of jerks around our school.Well I talk to you later,byez

Well, it's just me and my cat sitting here by the computer, well except for my sister who's sitting at the next computer over.We got picked up early from school today cause it was so rainy.It seems sort of peaceful, if we could just turn the damn t.v off.My grandma's sitting here and she's obsessed with her stupid soap opera's and right now this guy's making out with some old,old lady for $1,0000.!!!SICK!!!I wouldn't do that if someone paid me.All I'd end up doing is hanging myself after I got the money,with a golden rope.LOL!I wonder why Amber and my friend Michelle weren't here today?Amber's head probable exploded after yelling at her mom again.LOL!Michelle was also gone yesterday and I'm starting to worry cause she's going through some rough times right now with her mom.I hope she comes tomorrow,along with Amber.Lindzy and Amber are still fighting.I don't think Amber wants her back as a friend again.I get to work at PetsMart again this saturday,then spend the night at Amber's,then sunday we're going to Wire Warfare.It's going to be awsome!Some of my friends from school and Amber's boyfriend might be there.She's happy about that.I'm still failing math,57% F.That sucks bad!!I need a boyfriend bad.All my friends said Justin flirted way too much,but I didn't believe them.Should I?I don't know what to believe anymore....sigh.I honestly am not really enjoying my life right now,there's too many secrets in our family.I can't stand it!!No one in our family talks to each other and when we do it's either cause we are in trouble,mad,or have something mean to say.I mean,I'm the same way.I'm not gonna sit here and act like I don't cause I do.
